]</a><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">DEFRA </span><a href="Oxo-degradable%20plastics%20Q%20and%20A%20(Revised%2031/10/2013)"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt; text-decoration:underline">Oxo</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt; text-decoration:underline">-degradable plastics Q and A (Revised 31/10/2013)</span></a><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> Question 8</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> </span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">because EN13432 requires it to convert to CO</span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:Arial; font-size:5.33pt; vertical-align:sub">2</span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="color:#222222; font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">gas within 180 days</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> See </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">eg</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">Lusher</span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">, A.L., et al. Occurrence of </span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">microplastics</span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt"> in the gastrointestinal tract of pelagic and </span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">demersal</span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt"> fish from the English</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">Channel. Mar. </span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">Pollut</span><span style="font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">. Bull. (2012), </span><span style="color:#000066; font-family:AdvGulliv-R; font-size:7pt">http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.marpolbul.2012.11.028</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn14"></a><a href="#_ftnref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">Defined in</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">ASTM D883-11</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn15"></a><a href="#_ftnref15">[15]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">See </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">Vol</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">96 of the journal of Polymer Degradation &amp; Stability (2011) at pages 919-928, and Bibliography</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn16"></a><a href="#_ftnref16">[16]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> See Annex on Recycling</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn17"></a><a href="#_ftnref17">[17]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">EN 13432 </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">para</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">. A2.2</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn18"></a><a href="#_ftnref18">[18]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> </span><a name="_Toc366693609"></a><a name="_Toc366693537"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt; font-weight:bold">P7_TA-PROV(2013)0357</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 7.1pt; text-inden