oducts (Manufacturing, Sale and Usage) Regulations 2013</span></p><p style="font-size:8pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><a name="_ftn25"></a><a href="#_ftnref25">[25]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:8pt">Cabinet Decree No. 420/3 for the year 26/12/2009 Session No. 13</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p></body></html>